{"id": 2924, "genre": 1001, "title": "出门旅行，你觉得一个理想的旅伴是啥样？", "description": "一个玩友得具备啥素质你才想邀请ta同行？", "record_count": 3773, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190428152555oXJQrjS1nAuEKIiV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-01T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 342272, "content": "说好的时间行程能好好遵守，不要突然不去或突发奇想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535250}, {"id": 342273, "content": "玩到一块", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626764}, {"id": 342787, "content": "除了另一半，我不会和别人旅游，除了团建", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633295}, {"id": 342276, "content": "感觉可以对他放心地说出内心的真实想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031125}, {"id": 342793, "content": "爱我哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516691}, {"id": 341515, "content": "遇到麻烦不发脾气，依然能保持开心的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 892, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 341516, "content": "有分歧能友好协商解决", "image": null, "praise_count": 231, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 341517, "content": "一个上镜的手办可以说是最佳旅伴了", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 341518, "content": "口味一致，能吃到一块儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 207, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 342543, "content": "一起商讨出行攻略路线 查找最划算的机酒而不是全部都交给我 当然了你信任我这是另一回事 只是一个人全部搞定也很累 希望大家可以一起分担", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939196}, {"id": 342804, "content": "谈得来的人吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647882}, {"id": 342293, "content": "期待我们的第一次旅游🌲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195977}, {"id": 343061, "content": "理性对待游览的地方，失望也不要丧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650207}, {"id": 342552, "content": "遇到所有问题时都可以双方短时间内协商解决", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648575}, {"id": 342297, "content": "无人机 拍照 PS AE   万能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435439}, {"id": 343066, "content": "能谈天 能说地 能话唠 能自矜  不用你背上旅行的琐碎繁杂 但千万不要置身事外", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538954}, {"id": 342301, "content": "不墨迹，志同道合", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603779}, {"id": 342831, "content": "两个人可以商量 而不是把事儿全推到对方身上 自己和别人用手机聊天 全程没什么沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886560}, {"id": 342320, "content": "不要抱怨 这个非常重要！  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647738}, {"id": 342329, "content": "作息习惯一致！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647901}, {"id": 342586, "content": "首先，我的需要找一个人跟我一起出去玩……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648717}, {"id": 342075, "content": "会拍照", "image": null, "praise_count": 196, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 552467}, {"id": 342587, "content": "听我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868692}, {"id": 342076, "content": "好的心态，遇事不抱怨，不然很影响旅行的心情。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 436, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996680}, {"id": 342077, "content": "不粗心大意整幺蛾子", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264344}, {"id": 342078, "content": "冲动性的，喜欢冒险的", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386990}, {"id": 342079, "content": "幽默，遇到糟心事也能跳出当下，讲个冷笑话之类的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581744}, {"id": 342592, "content": "不会出现一方包办所有的事，另一方感受不到这份劳动、还把自己当做小公主柜门都不顺手关上、被劝帮着看路还嫌语气不好的情况", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289571}, {"id": 342081, "content": "消费观一致！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 654, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660957}, {"id": 342082, "content": "能动脑子出主意不是啥也不想还只会提意见的", "image": null, "praise_count": 362, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660957}, {"id": 342594, "content": "一个人上路不就好了.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613208}, {"id": 342083, "content": "能聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 155, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660957}, {"id": 342084, "content": "并不想和人一起旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377975}, {"id": 342086, "content": "消费观一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 342087, "content": "只喜欢一个人旅游。就连和伴侣出去玩后发觉根本不是不是我想要的旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1398653}, {"id": 342599, "content": "不乱丢垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310565}, {"id": 342088, "content": "我缺的不是旅游，而是一个值得一起的伴侣", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623654}, {"id": 342089, "content": "遇到问题，双方很好的沟通交流，找到满意的解决办法，而不是一味抱怨，全程", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357658}, {"id": 342091, "content": "在一块比较自在。", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 342092, "content": "开朗，乐观，不制造麻烦也不怕麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216372}, {"id": 342093, "content": "手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742602}, {"id": 342094, "content": "要求很低，不一路玩手机就行了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226002}, {"id": 342095, "content": "乐观，会拍照！三观、口味一致", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251362}, {"id": 342096, "content": "有共同兴趣爱好，有共同语言", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647335}, {"id": 342097, "content": "自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 342098, "content": "够机智，大方，豁达，靠谱，脑洞大，幽默乐观。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1183687}, {"id": 342099, "content": "随遇而安，有说有笑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393417}, {"id": 342100, "content": "当地人", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276287}, {"id": 342356, "content": "我带上他，他带上钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506746}, {"id": 342101, "content": "能一起去都想去的地方，也能短暂分开去各自想去的地方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879398}]}